# CubCloud Operations

Complete operational framework for CubCloud GPU inference infrastructure.

**ENTRY:** SSH access to CubCloud network via FortiClient VPN or Tailscale
**SUCCESS:** Services deployed, monitored, and performing at target SLA
**EXIT:** Clean shutdown preserving state, data, and configurations
**INVERSION:** If components fail, others continue with graceful degradation
**BOUNDS:** 4x H200 NVL (564GB) + 4x RTX PRO 6000 (384GB) = 948GB total VRAM

## Network Architecture

### Host Layout
| Host | IP | Purpose | Access |
|------|----|---------|---------|
| Gateway | 10.10.20.1 | Firewall/Router | Network admin |
| BMC/IPMI | 10.10.20.2 | Hardware management | IPMI console |
| **bwservermanager** | 10.10.20.10 | **Management + Services** | `ssh cubby@10.10.20.10` |
| H100 | 10.10.20.11 | Client GPU access | External clients |
| **bwh200server** | 10.10.20.12 | **8x GPU inference** | `ssh cubby@10.10.20.12` |

