## Troubleshooting Procedures

### Service Issues
| Issue | Symptoms | Resolution |
|-------|----------|------------|
| SGLang Service Down | Connection refused on sglang port | `ssh cubby@10.10.20.12 "sudo systemctl restart sglang-<name>"` |
| Service Down (.10) | Connection refused on mgmt port | `docker restart CONTAINER_ID` |
| HTTP 401 | Invalid token errors | Verify ZESTY_WORKER_TOKEN from secure source |
| **Bifrost 403 Forbidden** | **"Client error '403 Forbidden'" from chat completions** | **Update `gpu-services/BIFROST_KEY` with current internal key, restart container** |
| **Bifrost 403 Model Blocked** | **"Model not allowed for virtual key"** | **Run `./scripts/create-virtual-keys.sh`, update Infisical** |
| **Machine Identity Failed** | **Infisical auth errors, token expired** | **Run machine-identity.yml Ansible playbook** |
| **UFW Blocks SGLang** | **Bifrost can't reach .12 ports** | **Add UFW rules: `ufw allow from 10.10.20.10 to any port 30000:30007`** |
| **CubDen 500 errors** | **Internal server error on chat endpoints** | **Check forced RLS — handler likely uses `&state.pool` instead of `TenantTx`. Fix: use `TenantTx::begin(&state.pool, claims.org, claims.sub)`** |
| **CubDen rate limited** | **429 Too Many Requests on login** | **Wait 60s for rate limit window to clear. Tests should cache tokens, not re-login per module.** |
| Bifrost Unreachable | bifrost_reachable: false | Check port 8989, restart if needed |
| GPU OOM | CUDA out of memory | Check sglang instance health, restart affected GPU |
| Container Missing | docker ps shows no 8990 | Check Coolify deployment, trigger redeploy |
| cw-worker Down | No response on :8002 | `curl -X POST "http://10.10.20.10:8000/api/v1/applications/gosoc0w4808kgc004w8s0cw8/restart" -H "Authorization: Bearer $COOLIFY_TOKEN"` |
| cw-worker Health Fails During Task | Expected — single-threaded uvicorn blocks during 30min task execution | Normal behavior, not an error |

| Coolify deploy SSH fail | Permission denied on SSH | Check URL format (must be SCP-style `git@10.0.1.200:org/repo.git`), verify deploy key registered in Gitea, use Coolify API to create deploy keys |
| Coolify DecryptException | payload invalid or decryption failed | Raw key in DB — delete deploy key via API and recreate via Coolify UI |
| Port conflict | address already in use | Reserved ports: 5432 (default PostgreSQL), 5433 (CubDen PostgreSQL), 8081 (CubDen Backend) |
| CI workflow fails instantly | Runner starts but exits immediately | Runner image issue — ensure using `ubuntu-latest` label which has git+node+apt pre-installed |
